1
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:25,680
Tomorrow's land auction,

2
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:27,040
I've got you beat.

3
00:01:55,359 --> 00:01:56,239
Xiao Hui

4
00:01:56,799 --> 00:01:57,680
Stop fooling around.

5
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:00,640
Thinking of Xiao Hui at a time like this?

6
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:08,080
Tomorrow's land auction.

7
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,360
Xiao Yifan and He Junjie

8
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:11,199
only have authority up to 1.6 billion.

9
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:12,840
They can't authorize a single cent more.

10
00:02:13,879 --> 00:02:14,360
Well done.

11
00:02:15,919 --> 00:02:17,159
The moment you hear anything,

12
00:02:17,199 --> 00:02:18,599
notify Su Yuanyuan immediately.

13
00:02:19,319 --> 00:02:19,759
Understood.

14
00:02:55,879 --> 00:02:57,520
Mr. Xiao, you came to bid in person today.

15
00:02:57,960 --> 00:03:00,319
Wanhe Group values today's land auction.

16
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:03,360
Yes, Chairman Zheng gave specific orders.

17
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,800
Plot 6 sits right across from us.

18
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,120
So we must secure it.

19
00:03:06,159 --> 00:03:09,400
I hear Fang Group is bound to get Plot 6.

20
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,800
Then we'll see you at the auction.

21
00:03:17,159 --> 00:03:18,719
Good morning, real estate executives.

22
00:03:18,719 --> 00:03:21,199
I'm Hu Yue, the auctioneer for today.

23
00:03:21,639 --> 00:03:24,319
We'll begin today with Plot 6.

24
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:26,120
Plot 6 is, in this land auction,

25
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,680
the parcel with the best location.

26
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:29,159
Starting bid: 1.2 billion yuan.

27
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:31,560
Minimum raise: 1 million per bid.

28
00:03:31,759 --> 00:03:32,680
No upper limit.

29
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:34,360
Each bid must be made within one minute.

30
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:35,919
Gentlemen, bidding starts now.

31
00:03:36,919 --> 00:03:37,599
1.3 billion.

32
00:03:38,039 --> 00:03:40,400
The price jumps directly to 1.3 billion.

33
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:41,240
Any higher?

34
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:42,680
1.4 billion.

35
00:03:42,879 --> 00:03:45,120
We're now at 1.4 billion yuan.

36
00:03:45,759 --> 00:03:47,039
1.47 billion.

37
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:49,120
1.47 billion yuan.

38
00:03:49,479 --> 00:03:51,319
1.47 billion going once.

39
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,159
1.475 billion.

40
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,360
1.478.

41
00:03:54,759 --> 00:03:56,159
1.48 billion.

42
00:03:56,599 --> 00:03:58,000
1.485 billion.

43
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,719
1.485 billion yuan.

44
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:03,039
A bid of 1.485 billion. Any higher?

45
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,039
The competition seems fierce.

46
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,599
Everyone's hesitating.

47
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,919
Remember, one minute per bid.

48
00:04:08,919 --> 00:04:10,000
1.485 billion.

49
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:13,520
1.49 billion.

50
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,680
1.491 billion.

51
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:17,399
1.491 billion yuan.

52
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:20,199
1.491 billion going once.

53
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:23,839
1.492 billion.

54
00:04:24,839 --> 00:04:25,920
At this rate,

55
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:28,120
our 1.6 billion limit won't be enough.

56
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:30,839
Don't worry.

57
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:32,199
Chairman Zheng has sent Han Lin

58
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,879
to deliver the temporary authorization.

59
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:37,079
Get it to Xiao Yifan right away.

60
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,000
Yes, Chairman Zheng.

61
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:44,720
Bidding against me for land?

62
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,279
You're still too green.

63
00:04:46,759 --> 00:04:48,480
Seven years ago I failed to crush you,

64
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:49,959
but today,

65
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,560
let's see how you'll outbid me.

66
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:58,040
No one leaves tonight until this is done.

67
00:05:32,439 --> 00:05:33,360
What's wrong?

68
00:05:43,079 --> 00:05:43,800
Hello?

69
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:44,560
There's been an accident at the site.

70
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:45,680
What?

71
00:05:47,879 --> 00:05:48,319
It's him.

72
00:05:48,519 --> 00:05:49,839
He's the head guy around here.

73
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:52,879
They've been trapped inside for hours!

74
00:05:53,079 --> 00:05:54,639
Do our lives even mean anything to you?

75
00:05:54,959 --> 00:05:55,879
Everyone, calm down first.

76
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,160
Let's rescue the trapped people first.

77
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:58,800
Right, get the injured into ambulances.

78
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:00,439
My brother's already in the hospital.

79
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:01,639
None of us know right now

80
00:06:01,639 --> 00:06:02,439
how badly they're injured.

81
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:03,560
I'm asking you,

82
00:06:03,639 --> 00:06:04,879
their medical bills and lost wages,

83
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:05,800
who's going to pay?

84
00:06:05,879 --> 00:06:06,560
Who's going to settle this?

85
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:07,279
Right.

86
00:06:07,319 --> 00:06:08,120
Who's going to take responsibility?

87
00:06:08,319 --> 00:06:09,439
Why are you all crowding around me?

88
00:06:09,639 --> 00:06:10,759
Hurry in and rescue them!

89
00:06:10,959 --> 00:06:11,680
If treatment is delayed,

90
00:06:11,759 --> 00:06:12,639
who can bear that responsibility?

91
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:13,959
After such a major accident,

92
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,040
you owe us an explanation.

93
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:15,600
Manager Xiao,

94
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,319
don't forget,

95
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:18,040
you started at the bottom too.

96
00:06:21,199 --> 00:06:22,199
Please rest assured,

97
00:06:22,439 --> 00:06:24,439
I'll find out the cause of this accident.

98
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,079
In the meantime,

99
00:06:26,279 --> 00:06:27,240
the medical expenses this time

100
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,759
will be covered by our company.

101
00:06:28,759 --> 00:06:31,000
It's not just medical bills, Manager Xiao.

102
00:06:31,279 --> 00:06:32,199
If this incident

103
00:06:32,199 --> 00:06:33,360
causes the project to be halted,

104
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:35,160
who's going to compensate our losses?

105
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:37,560
Right, we're all from the same village.

106
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:38,879
With something this serious happening,

107
00:06:39,199 --> 00:06:41,040
how do we explain this to their families?

108
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:42,480
Please trust me.

109
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:44,160
I will give you a just

110
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,279
and fair resolution.

111
00:06:45,279 --> 00:06:46,279
Words aren't enough.

112
00:06:46,279 --> 00:06:47,480
We're not buying your empty promises.

113
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:49,199
Put it in writing right now.

114
00:06:49,199 --> 00:06:49,800
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

115
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,000
In writing! Compensation in writing!

116
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:51,639
Where's Fang Bing?

117
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,439
He's the head contractor on this job.

118
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:54,720
After such a serious incident,

119
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:55,800
he still hasn't shown his face.

120
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,279
Tell him to get his ass over here now!

121
00:07:06,399 --> 00:07:08,639
Get me 500,000 in cash, fast!

122
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:09,920
500,000?

123
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:10,680
What for?

124
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:11,759
Keeping a mistress?

125
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,639
Cut the crap, I don't have time for this.

126
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:17,040
What's your problem?

127
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:18,279
Don't take it out on me.

128
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:20,399
Don't think I don't know your shady deeds.

129
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,720
You've blown through all my money.

130
00:07:24,279 --> 00:07:26,000
The tower crane on my site collapsed.

131
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,720
Many were hurt. I need to disappear now.

132
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:33,720
The crane collapsed?

133
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:35,319
With an accident this big, can you run?

134
00:07:36,199 --> 00:07:37,439
Then what do you suggest I do?

135
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:40,920
You're the project manager.

136
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,000
You're the only one we'll deal with.

137
00:07:42,199 --> 00:07:42,959
If you don't pay up,

138
00:07:42,959 --> 00:07:44,040
you're not leaving here today.

139
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:44,600
Right!

140
00:07:44,879 --> 00:07:46,279
Pay up!

141
00:07:46,279 --> 00:07:47,920
Pay up!

142
00:07:49,319 --> 00:07:50,959
Pay up!

143
00:07:54,279 --> 00:07:55,040
Time's running out.

144
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:58,079
1.595 billion.

145
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:01,600
1.595 billion.

146
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,879
1.595 billion going once.

147
00:08:04,839 --> 00:08:05,480
1.6 billion.

148
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:07,439
Wow!

149
00:08:07,439 --> 00:08:09,759
The price is sky-high!

150
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,639
1.6 billion. It's getting tense.

151
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:13,839
The price has reached 1.6 billion.

152
00:08:14,399 --> 00:08:15,720
1.605 billion.

153
00:08:16,199 --> 00:08:16,879
We're done for.

154
00:08:17,319 --> 00:08:18,519
There's no way we can get Plot 6 now.

155
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,759
1.605 billion.

156
00:08:20,319 --> 00:08:21,279
Why isn't it here yet?

157
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:22,920
Can we even count on Han Lin?

158
00:08:24,399 --> 00:08:27,439
Chairman Zheng gave a 1.8B authorization.

159
00:08:27,639 --> 00:08:29,360
He told me to rush it to the auction site.

160
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:31,519
1.8 billion?

161
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:34,240
Your company is really going all in.

162
00:08:34,399 --> 00:08:35,919
I don't care how you do it.

163
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:38,639
That authorization can't reach Xiao Yifan.

164
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:44,039
Hello?

165
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:44,919
Hello?

166
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:57,799
1.605 billion going twice.

167
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:26,759
Auntie, don't worry.

168
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:29,320
Plot 6 will definitely go to your company.

169
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:49,039
1.6 billion is their ceiling.

170
00:09:49,559 --> 00:09:50,919
He can only sit there and stew.

171
00:09:53,919 --> 00:09:55,840
1.605 billion going for the third time.

172
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:58,320
Sold!

173
00:09:59,799 --> 00:10:01,200
Congratulations to the Fang Group.

174
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:06,000
The Fang Group has won Plot 6.

175
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:07,720
Next, we will be moving on to

176
00:10:07,919 --> 00:10:09,159
the auction for Plot 7.

177
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,360
Please take a moment to prepare.

178
00:10:11,519 --> 00:10:13,000
We evaluated Plot 6 so carefully.

179
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:15,919
A 1.6 billion premium is already steep.

180
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:17,600
Fang Shuxiu bid even higher than us.

181
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:18,559
Ruthless.

182
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:20,679
What did you expect?

183
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,600
What the hell is going on?

184
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:25,120
Why does Han Lin choke at key moments?

185
00:10:27,159 --> 00:10:27,840
Junjie.

186
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,320
Don't get worked up just yet.

187
00:10:29,879 --> 00:10:31,159
The real show is still to come.

188
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:32,639
What damn show is left?

189
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:34,120
Don't tell me we're going after

190
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:35,360
that godforsaken Plot 7.

191
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:37,279
Why not?

192
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:38,639
Take what others discard,

193
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:39,960
discard what others take.

194
00:10:40,759 --> 00:10:41,399
Seriously?

195
00:10:41,679 --> 00:10:42,360
Have you lost your mind?

196
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:47,600
Are you hiding something from me?

197
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:49,480
Do you still remember

198
00:10:49,879 --> 00:10:51,320
the site accident from seven years ago?

199
00:10:52,919 --> 00:10:54,759
Seven years ago.

200
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:56,600
If I hadn't risked my life to save you,

201
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:58,639
you might already be...

202
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:03,159
Pay up!

203
00:11:05,759 --> 00:11:07,200
What are you doing? Out of my way!

204
00:11:07,679 --> 00:11:09,240
Who the hell do you think you are?

205
00:11:09,679 --> 00:11:11,039
I'm head of the safety department.

206
00:11:11,039 --> 00:11:11,879
So you tell me who I am.

207
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:14,120
If we don't get paid today,

208
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:14,919
nobody's leaving!

209
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:16,840
A state has laws, a family has rules.

210
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:18,120
And a worksite has its own rules.

211
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:19,559
If you want your money,

212
00:11:19,559 --> 00:11:20,639
then don't cause trouble here.

213
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,879
Whoever wants to throw a punch,

214
00:11:22,879 --> 00:11:23,600
come on!

215
00:11:24,759 --> 00:11:25,639
Fight me one-on-one.

216
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:26,120
Come on!

217
00:11:26,559 --> 00:11:27,440
Brother, brother!

218
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:28,960
Getting the compensation comes first.

219
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,440
Compensation.

220
00:11:32,279 --> 00:11:33,320
Everyone, break it up.

221
00:11:33,759 --> 00:11:34,559
Let's head to the hospital first

222
00:11:34,799 --> 00:11:36,120
to check on our injured brothers.

223
00:11:36,759 --> 00:11:37,320
This matter,

224
00:11:37,559 --> 00:11:38,519
I will get to the bottom of it.

225
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:40,480
When the time comes, the compensation

226
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:41,519
will not be short by a single cent.

227
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:43,159
All right, everyone, disperse.

228
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:46,720
Business is a battlefield.

229
00:11:47,879 --> 00:11:49,879
The site accident seven years ago,

230
00:11:50,039 --> 00:11:51,840
someone had to be pulling the strings.

231
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:56,960
Still wet behind the ears.

232
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,799
What have you got to take me on?

233
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:00,799
Xiao Yifan,

234
00:12:01,159 --> 00:12:03,720
sooner or later, you'll be at my feet.
